divs: Sighting DetailsThis picture was obtained from a friend. It is of he and a friend. They did not witness the event, but found the anomaly in the photo. They report that they have the original negatives in storage and that the disc does not appear on pre or post pics. I asked them permission to report this, and they are open to answering questions. Coincidentally the one who took the photo reported that she began having her migraines shortly after this photo was taken...
